—fragment of stem (A); cladial hydrotheca in lateral view (B); frontal view of two cladial hydrothecae, note presence of either two (left) or one (right) axillar nematothecae (C); different shapes of lateral nematotheca (D); gonotheca (E); nematocysts (F). G and H: 
